data.description: Looking for that perfect home that is central to all surrounding areas but outside of the hustle and bustle? This full brick home sits on 1 acre and is truly move in ready. The inviting open floorplan gives you the all the space you need with large bedrooms, new flooring, upgraded kitchen and bathrooms. The master bedroom is sure to be the perfect size with a large on suite bath and walk in closet. Enjoy cooking out on the secluded back patio. Convenience is an understatement as it is located only minutes to Lincoln, Pell City, Talladega and I-20. There are two marinas within a 5-10 minute drive to launch from for fun summer days on the lake. When scheduling your appointment, don't forget to ask about the option for a 3% seller credit with our preferred lender, Coosa Valley Mortgage NMLS 198757.
